  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DCAFFE10-22CE-0135-48B3-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Update Course Details </strong>button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
